Chesapeake Asset Management, LLC










Managing DirectorsMaureen T. Orlando, Managing Director & Chief of Operations.Prior to joining Chesapeake, Ms. Orlando was a Marketing/Account Administrator at Delphi Asset Management, Account Administrator at Weiss Peck and Greer, and an Account Administrator at Neuberger Berman. Ms. Orlando received her Bachelor of Business Administration degree from St. Bonaventure University in 1988.Gerasimos J. Efthimiatos, Managing Director & Portfolio Manager.Prior to joining Chesapeake, Mr. Efthimiatos was the Chief Investment Officer of Sigma Rose, a Partner of Habrok Capital Partners, a Senior Analyst at Axiom Investments, and an Equity Options Trader at Arbitrade Holdings LLC. Mr. Efthimiatos received his Master of Business Administration degree from Cornell University in 2003 and his integrated Bachelor/Master of Engineering degree from the University of London in 1997.





















