Welcome to Chesapeake Asset Management

We are an independent financial advisory practice specializing in wealth management for individuals, families and businesses. Through our association with the Wells Fargo Advisors Financial Network, we offer the independence and specialization backed by one of the nation’s premier financial services firm.  Our team of professionals are dedicated to providing every client with targeted comprehensive financial advice to help meet their needs.We invite you to contact one of our professionals and explore the variety of information and tools on our site.  For more information or to schedule an appointment, give us a call at 804-335-0645 or toll free 866-544-7751, click on the Request for Info link or email one of our professionals.









